name: Create user with different names and jobs (example #1)
fullName: Create user with different names and jobs (example #1)

steps.name: Given I have the POST endpoint
When I send a POST request with name "Bob" and job "Designer"
request ("{ method: 'POST', url: 'https://reqres.in/api/users', headers: { 'x-api-key': 'reqres-free-v1' }, body: { name: 'Bob', job: 'Designer' }, failOnStatusCode: false }")
Then the response status should be 201
Then the response should contain a user ID
